# Dify Apps — YAML (DSL) exports
#
# Export your Dify apps from the Studio (Settings → Export DSL) and commit the
# YAML files here. This directory IS the source of truth for agent/workflow
# versioning, per the operational non-negotiables in CLAUDE.md.
#
# Suggested naming: {tenant-slug}__{app-kind}.yml
#   example:  acme__support-agent.yml
#             acme__rag-kb.yml
#             beta-co__scheduling-workflow.yml
